      *                                                               *
      *  LUC139 - UCI Italian returns upgrade to FM2.1                *
      *  CER008 - Base Italian Features Upgrade to MidasPlus          *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     FSDCUT1L0IF  E           K        DISK
      ** Customer details extended file for Italy  - Retrieval index -
      *
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
      ** Array containing Copyright statement
      *
     E                    NARR    1   2 80
      ** Fields narratives array
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
     IBLLINE      DS                            264
     I                                        1 132 BLLIN1
     I                                      133 264 BLLIN2
      ** Extended info from Italian Customer details extended file,
      ** passed as parameter
      *
     IPRTLIN      DS                            132
     I                                        1  50 NARRAT
     I                                       51  66 FIELD
      ** DS to define printing line content
      *
     ISCSARD    E DSSCSARDPD
      ** SCSARDD0 - SAR Descriptions record format data structure
      *
     IDSFDY     E DSDSFDY
      ** First DS for access programs, short data structure
      *
      *
      ** Program Start
      ** Initialize return parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEL*OFF      PFAIL
      *
      ** Access extended customer record
      *
     C           PCUST     CHAINSDCUT1L0             89
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *OFF
      *
      ** Set up extended lines
      ** 1.- First printing line : '004:Redidenza'
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   PRTLIN
     C                     MOVELNARR,1    NARRAT
     C                     MOVELBBA004    FIELD
     C                     MOVELPRTLIN    BLLIN1
      *
      ** 2.- Second printing line : 'RAD Charge Code'
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   PRTLIN
     C                     MOVELNARR,2    NARRAT
     C                     MOVELPRTLIN    BLLIN2
      *
      ** Setup return parameter
      *
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL*ON       PFAIL
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Return to caller program
      *
     C                     RETRN
      *
      ** Program End
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *INZSR - Initial Subroutine                                  *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      A@CPY  80
      *
      ** Define parameters list
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PCUST   6
     C                     PARM           BLLINE
     C                     PARM           PFAIL   1
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *****************************************************************
